==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Paymaster
<hw>Pay"mas`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who pays; one
who compensates, rewards, or requites; specifically, an officer or agent
of a government, a corporation, or an employer, whose duty it is to pay
salaries, wages, etc., and keep account of the same.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Paymaster-general</ent>⟦br⟧
